{"tid":1563420,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港隊]我願榮光歸香港正式成為香港國歌嘅唯一方法","createTime":"2019-09-12T11:38:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T06:58:33.000Z","uid":8954,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"bf285acf4745c169fa9ea5bebceac39405c8b49a","tid":1563420,"uid":8954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:38:05.000Z","msg":"咁多位 FIFA 世界盃外圍賽<br />\n香港隊每場賽前都會奏支那國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但你地又知唔知 每個國家係唔一定要播奏國歌 可以自由選擇代表嘅歌<br />\n<br />\n例子: England vs Scotland<br />\nScotland都無跟英格蘭唱God save the queen<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9rr8KNc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9rr8KNc.png&h=83bdf855&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0Z2lR_qvZYk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0Z2lR_qvZYk&d=S%2BP5iCTdX9iTDztVuYOIbwy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=d6d41ed2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0Z2lR_qvZYk</a><br />\n<br />\n齊齊集氣 推到足總響下場 (11月14日) 香港隊主場對巴林<br />\n轉我願榮光歸香港做國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"684dfdba86580ada07c38ae4e2da8c54efc9eff2","tid":1563420,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:38:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/a